@More aggressive strip flags for non debug kernels; this is a noop on some
architectures, but saves a few dozen KB on alpha and ppc.

ok deraadt@@
@
text
@d90 3
a92 2
		echo cp $@@ $@@.gdb; rm -f $@@.gdb; cp $@@ $@@.gdb; \
		echo ${STRIP} ${STRIPFLAGS} $@@; ${STRIP} ${STRIPFLAGS} $@@
@


